Growing Up I Literally Used To Think This Guy Was SUPER MAN! I Still Kinda Feel The Same Way. He Ran Everything. He Owned Everything. He Knew Everybody From Pastors To Prisoners To Politicians To Homeless To Rich To Poor. Everyone Respected This Guy. I Used To Abuse The Words “Ima Tell My Dad”. Whenever I Said That The Vibe Would Change In My Favor. I Didn’t Know Why I Just Knew It Would Work. The Only People It Didn’t Work On Was My Family. They Would Be Like STFU CALL HIM😂😂. This Is The Coolest Dopest Person I’ve Ever Met. ❤️U Pop
